description: Nextleaf Solutions Ltd., a cannabis extraction technology company, develops and licenses technology for the extraction, distillation, and formulation of cannabinoids in Canada. The company extracts, distills, purifies, delivers, and wholesales CBD oils and THC cannabinoid ingredients; researches and develops cannabis infused products, vapes, ingestible concentrates, and specialty extracts; and provides extraction services. It also focuses on the development and commercialization of psychoactive compounds. The company was formerly known as Legion Metals Corp. and changed its name to Nextleaf Solutions Ltd. Nextleaf Solutions Ltd. was founded in 2015 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
